{"tid":1716254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫人停運物資","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:15:30.000Z","uid":77393,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8561c615a84ba7abb361106c405299c5550b6a2c","tid":1716254,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"物資現時過多滯留 未分得切係正常<br />\n因為好多手足不斷運入去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但絕對冇可能叫人停運<br />\n一打起仗上嚟<br />\n貶下眼就會用晒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n建議大家可以提出主要需要邊方面嘅物資<br />\n其中一定係魔法類 同 急救類比較需要存貨<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家要謹記<br />\n當有需要用物資嘅嗰刻<br />\n運入去嘅風險同時大幅增加<br />\n甚至運唔到入去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而我哋刻下要做嘅<br />\n係趁未開戰之前<br />\n提升物資分配嘅效率</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"33ebd86024c1f3fe01b84d948d89dc17ddaab4f9","tid":1716254,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:51:01.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"16a9898b7a391259afe98a62053a976a4605e5bf","tid":1716254,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2ffbab6d84b358959a235afe66978fe132a1c48","tid":1716254,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7958f58777886c81e667a86b23e683fb6bfc9c0f","tid":1716254,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"457f93af1e99a756548de05ba6116de088242304","tid":1716254,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"今日下午沿途都有人傳話<br />\n支援市民絡繹不絕"},{"pid":"d6e2c455fe8bf25d47704f90c4f3f5994a6aecd3","tid":1716254,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r